Resource "Money" units
Entity "Alice"
Entity "Bob"
Flow "Money" from "Alice" to "Bob" quantity 10
policy VacuousForall as: forall i in instances: (i.amount <= 1)
policy ExistsNull as: exists f in flows: (f.category = "premium")
policy ExistsUniqueFlow as: exists_unique f in flows: (f.quantity >= 0)
